			Well, I will put my 2cp's in:<BR>
The one and ONLY time I saw Bugglegupp <BR>
(female Troll), was as my human ranger in his<BR>
11th season. I was zoning in from LF and there she<BR>
 was right there at zone entrance in SF. At first,<BR>
I didn't think anything of it.. I thought it was a<BR>
player, unitil it got closer and commenced to <BR>
beating the tar out of me.  I conned it and it was <BR>
blue. I don't remember if it was casting spells or <BR>
not but it DID poison. I was down real low in <BR>
health so I ran for zone.. (note: I was at full <BR>
health b4 it attacked), well I made it to LF, BUT<BR>
the poison did its trick and I died right on other<BR>
side in LF. I didn't even have time to cast heal, <BR>
cause I had just barely a sliver of health left.<BR>
I turned and ran at 2 bubbles... but she <BR>
backstabbed me a BUNCH of points.<BR>
<BR>
Its funny... cause I have a 14 gnome mage.. and<BR>
I played him up to level 12 in SF, and I had NEVER<BR>
ran across her or any other Troll npc's there.<BR>
<BR>
Live and learn.. <BR>
She was a VERY TOUGH blue!!<BR>
<BR>
I have my ranger now his 15 season... and I just<BR>
got back to Faydwer.. so maybe I will run into <BR>
her again... payback is MOFO!! muhahhaha<BR>

