			One time I was grouped with a friend at the kobold camp and as I was meditating I started hearing the clanking sound of a fight so I got up and turned to see my friend fight a giant female troll and she was hitting him HARD, we were both around lvl 5 or 6 I think, it only took a matter of seconds before he was dead and a minute later so was I. Once I came back naked to my bound point I shouted that there was some big ole' nasty troll in the newbie zone of steamfont that was ridiculously high for that area then I started hearing shouts of other gnomes who had been victims of her rampage.<BR>
<BR>
Well, luckily, a high lvl who was camping guards was nice enough to end the troll's killing spree and after she finished looting the troll (she said there was nothing of value on it) about 3 or 4 gnomes stood by the corpse waiting for a chance to get the goods. Being the master looter that I am I got the chance to get the &quot;goods&quot;, all I saw was a rusty dagger and an iron pellet so I picked up the iron pellet and have carried it for around 6 or 7 levels having no clue what quest it was for ever since that day.
