<BR>
Bugglegupp<BR>
Level 11 Female Troll<BR>
Hits like a 12 and has a lot of HP<BR>
Drops a rusty dagger and iron pellets<BR>
<BR>
You take the pellets to the magician in the library in ak'anon ( I think his name is tergon, but he is the gnome in the door room on the left of the main entrance). He will give you some gold, a level 8 spell (I think) and faction. He then say he may have [other tasks] for you. <BR>
<BR>
If you do the [other tasks] he says he needs his spell book retrivied from his brother and gives you a letter to take to him. I haven't done this part but I will let you know.
